Document: AudioEffectLowPassFilter
Path: godot/classes/class_audioeffectlowpassfilter.rst
Summary: A low-pass filter that attenuates high frequencies and allows lower frequencies to pass unchanged, used to muffle sounds.

A "low-pass" filter attenuates frequencies higher than AudioEffectFilter.cutoff_hz and allows lower frequencies to pass unchanged. This filter can be used to muffle sounds.
